  "answer_expr": "polyint",
  "steps": [
    "Use the power rule: integral of x^n dx = x^(n+1)/(n+1).",
    "Evaluate from 0 to {b}: [{b}^({n}+1) / ({n}+1)] - [0^({n}+1)/({n}+1)].",
    "= {b_pow} / {n_plus_1} = {answer_polyint}."
  ],
